to thin strips and separate the cloves from the head of garlic and cut a slit on each one, leaving the skins on","name":"In the meantime, thinly slice the onion, cut the bell peppers into thin strips and separate the cloves from the head of garlic and cut a slit on each one, leaving the skins on","url":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-poor-mans-sweet-potatoes-recipe\\/#wprm-recipe-16652-step-0-1"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add the cut onions, bell peppers and garlic into the hot fry pan, mix together so everything is coated in the olive oil, then mix every 1 to 2 minutes so everything evenly sautes","name":"Add the cut onions, bell peppers and garlic into the hot fry pan, mix together so everything is coated in the olive oil, then mix every 1 to 2 minutes so everything evenly sautes","url":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-poor-mans-sweet-potatoes-recipe\\/#wprm-recipe-16652-step-0-2"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"While the vegetables are cooking, cut the sweet potatoes (skins on) into bite-size pieces that are 2 cm thick (3\\/4 inch)","name":"While the vegetables are cooking, cut the sweet potatoes (skins on) into bite-size pieces that are 2 cm thick (3\\/4 inch)","url":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-poor-mans-sweet-potatoes-recipe\\/#wprm-recipe-16652-step-0-3"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"After 5 to 6 minutes and the vegetables are lightly sauteed, add in the chopped sweet potatoes, mix together, then mix every 3 to 4 minutes so everything evenly cooks","name":"After 5 to 6 minutes and the vegetables are lightly sauteed, add in the chopped sweet potatoes, mix together, then mix every 3 to 4 minutes so everything evenly cooks","url":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-poor-mans-sweet-potatoes-recipe\\/#wprm-recipe-16652-step-0-4"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Once the sweet potatoes are cooked through, about 25 to 30 minutes, season generously with sea salt and just a dash of black pepper, gently mix together, then remove from the hea