"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https:\\/\\/secure.gravatar.com\\/avatar\\/1e8709ffbf762ce98cf11b19eed76154f6088c5b0eb5ff06afbe0fec31ed969c?s=96&d=mm&r=g","url":"https:\\/\\/secure.gravatar.com\\/avatar\\/1e8709ffbf762ce98cf11b19eed76154f6088c5b0eb5ff06afbe0fec31ed969c?s=96&d=mm&r=g","contentUrl":"https:\\/\\/secure.gravatar.com\\/avatar\\/1e8709ffbf762ce98cf11b19eed76154f6088c5b0eb5ff06afbe0fec31ed969c?s=96&d=mm&r=g","caption":"Spain on a Fork"},"logo":{"@id":"https:\\/\\/secure.gravatar.com\\/avatar\\/1e8709ffbf762ce98cf11b19eed76154f6088c5b0eb5ff06afbe0fec31ed969c?s=96&d=mm&r=g"},"sameAs":["https:\\/\\/spainonafork.wpengine.com"]},{"@type":"Recipe","name":"Spanish Garlic &amp; Vinegar Soup","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Albert Bevia @ Spain on a Fork"},"description":"","datePublished":"2024-01-05T15:00:00+00:00","image":["https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/01\\/image1-3-11.png","https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/01\\/image1-3-11-500x500.png","https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/01\\/image1-3-11-500x375.png","https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/01\\/image1-3-11-480x270.png"],"recipeYield":["4"],"prepTime":"PT10M","cookTime":"PT25M","recipeIngredient":["1\\/4 cup extra virgin olive oil (60 ml)","6 slices baguette (1 inch \\/ 2.50 cm thick each)","6 cloves garlic thinly sliced","1 tbsp sherry vinegar (15 ml)","2 tsp sweet smoked Spanish paprika (5 grams)","1\\/2 tsp dried thyme (.50 grams)","6 cups vegetable broth (1400 ml)","4 eggs","2 tbsp chopped fresh parsley (8 grams)","2 cloves garlic roughy chopped","pinch sea salt","dash black pepper"],"recipeInstructions":[{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Heat a stock pot with a medium heat and add in the olive oil","name":"Heat a stock pot with a medium heat and add in the olive oil","url":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-garlic-and-vinegar-soup-recipe\\/#wprm-recipe-16160-step-0-0"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Once the olive oil is nice and hot, add in the sliced garlic, mix continuously, after 30 seconds to 1 minute and the garlic is fragrant, add in the slices of baguette, continue to mix continuously","name":"Once the olive oil is nice and hot, add in the sliced garlic, mix continuously, after 30 seconds to 1 minute and the garlic is fragrant, add in the slices of baguette, continue to mix continuously","url":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-garlic-and-vinegar-soup-recipe\\/#wprm-recipe-16160-step-0-1"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"After 3 to 4 minutes and the garlic and slices of baguette are lightly golden fried, add in the sherry vinegar, paprika, dried thyme and season with sea salt &amp; black pepper, quickly mix together, then add in the broth and raise to a high heat","name":"After 3 to 4 minutes and the garlic and slices of baguette are lightly golden fried, add in the sherry vinegar, paprika, dried thyme and season with sea salt &amp; black pepper, quickly mix together, then add in the broth and raise to a high heat","url":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-garlic-and-vinegar-soup-recipe\\/#wprm-recipe-16160-step-0-2"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"In the meantime, add the chopped garlic into a mortar, along with the chopped parsley and a kiss of sea salt, using a pestle, pound down on the mixture until you get a paste-like texture","name":"In the meantime, add the chopped garlic into a mortar, along with the chopped parsley and a kiss of sea salt, using a pestle, pound down on the mixture until you get a paste-like texture","url":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-garlic-and-vinegar-soup-recipe\\/#wprm-recipe-16160-step-0-3"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Once the broth comes to a boil, add the garlic and parsley mixture, gently mix it into the soup, then place a lid on the stock pot and lower to a low-medium heat","name":"Once the broth comes to a boil, add the garlic and parsley mixture, gently mix it into the soup, then place a lid on the stock pot and lower to a low-medium heat","url":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-garlic-and-vinegar-soup-recipe\\/#wprm-recipe-16160-step-0-4"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"After 10 minutes remove the lid, using a large wooden spoon or spatula, push down on the slices of baguette and break them apart into smaller chunks, then crack in the eggs into the soup, all evenly spaced out, place the lid back on the pan and simmer for 3 to 4 minutes or until the egg whites are just cooked through, then remove from the heat","name":"After 10 minutes remove the lid, using a large wooden spoon or spatula, push down on the slices of baguette and break them apart into smaller chunks, then crack in the eggs into the soup, all evenly spaced out, place the lid back on the pan and simmer for 3 to 4 minutes or until the egg whites are just cooked through, then remove from the heat","url":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-garlic-and-vinegar-soup-recipe\\/#wprm-recipe-16160-step-0-5"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Transfer the soup into shallow bowls, serve at once, enjoy!","name":"Transfer the soup into shallow bowls, serve at once, enjoy!","url":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-garlic-and-vinegar-soup-recipe\\/#wprm-recipe-16160-step-0-6"}],"recipeCategory":["Soup"],"recipeCuisine":["Spanish"],"nutrition":{"@type":"NutritionInformation","calories":"343 kcal","carbohydrateContent":"31 g","proteinContent":"12 g","fatContent":"19 g","saturatedFatContent":"4 g","transFatContent":"0.02 g","cholesterolContent":"164 mg","sodiumContent":"944 mg","fiberContent":"3 g","sugarContent":"4 g","unsaturatedFatContent":"15 g","servingSize":"1 serving"},"@id":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-garlic-and-vinegar-soup-recipe\\/#recipe","isPartOf":{"@id":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-garlic-and-vinegar-soup-recipe\\/#article"},"mainEntityOfPage":"https:\\/\\/spainonafork.com\\/spanish-garlic-and-vinegar-soup-recipe\\/"}]}',
                'image' => 'https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/image1-3-11.png?fit=750%2C750&ssl=1',
            'ingredients' => '["1\\/4 cup extra virgin olive oil (60 ml)","6 slices baguette (1 inch \\/ 2.50 cm thick each)","6 cloves garlic thinly sliced","1 tbsp sherry vinegar (15 ml)","2 tsp sweet smoked Spanish paprika (5 grams)","1\\/2 tsp dried thyme (.50 grams)","6 cups vegetable broth (1400 ml)","4 eggs","2 tbsp chopped fresh parsley (8 grams)","2 cloves garlic roughy chopped","pinch sea salt","dash black pepper"]',
                'directions' => '["Heat a stock pot with a medium heat and add in the olive oil","Once the olive oil is nice and hot, add in the sliced garlic, mix continuously, after 30 seconds to 1 minute and the garlic is fragrant, add in the slices of baguette, continue to mix continuously","After 3 to 4 minutes and the garlic and slices of baguette are lightly golden fried, add in the sherry vinegar, paprika, dried thyme and season with sea salt &amp; black pepper, quickly mix together, then add in the broth and raise to a high heat","In the meantime, add the chopped garlic into a mortar, along with the chopped parsley and a kiss of sea salt, using a pestle, pound down on the mixture until you get a paste-like texture","Once the broth comes to a boil, add the garlic and parsley mixture, gently mix it into the soup, then place a lid on the stock pot and lower to a low-medium heat","After 10 minutes remove the lid, using a large wooden spoon or spatula, push down on the slices of baguette and break them apart into smaller chunks, then crack in the eggs into the soup, all evenly spaced out, place the lid back on the pan and simmer for 3 to 4 minutes or until the egg whites are just cooked through, then remove from the heat","Transfer the soup into shallow bowls, serve at once, enjoy!"]',
                'nutrition' => '[{"@type":"NutritionInformation","calories":"343 kcal","carbohydrateContent":"31 g","proteinContent":"12 g","fatContent":"19 g","saturatedFatContent":"4 g","transFatContent":"0.02 g","cholesterolContent":"164 mg","sodiumContent":"944 mg","fiberContent":"3 g","sugarContent":"4 g","unsaturatedFatContent":"15 g","servingSize":"1 serving"}]',
