er made, it is so flavorful. It is also packed","breadcrumb":{"@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#breadcrumb"},"mainEntity":[{"@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#faq-question-1691085282993"},{"@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#faq-question-1692026331353"},{"@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#faq-question-1729621560710"}],"inLanguage":"en-US","potentialAction":[{"@type":"ReadAction","target":["https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/"]}]},{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#primaryimage","url":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/12\\/IMG_2024-12-10-135841.jpeg","contentUrl":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/12\\/IMG_2024-12-10-135841.jpeg","width":1200,"height":1200,"caption":"tuscan lentil soup with sundried tomatoes"},{"@type":"BreadcrumbList","@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#breadcrumb","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"Fall Favorites","item":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/category\\/fall\\/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"name":"Tuscan Lentil Soup with Sundried Tomatoes"}]},{"@type":"WebSite","@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/#website","url":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/","name":"Avocado Skillet","description":"Healthy Plant Based Recipes and Wellness","publisher":{"@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/#organization"},"potentialAction":[{"@type":"SearchAction","target":{"@type":"EntryPoint","urlTemplate":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/?s={search_term_string}"},"query-input":"required name=search_term_string"}],"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Organization","@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/#organization","name":"Avocado Skillet","url":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/#\\/schema\\/logo\\/image\\/","url":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/01\\/logo_digital_3_50.jpg","contentUrl":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2022\\/01\\/logo_digital_3_50.jpg","width":649,"height":132,"caption":"Avocado Skillet"},"image":{"@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/#\\/schema\\/logo\\/image\\/"},"sameAs":["https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/avocado_skillet\\/","https:\\/\\/www.pinterest.com\\/avocadoskillet\\/","https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/avocadoskillet\\/"]},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/#\\/schema\\/person\\/9672699ccfbdf3802f89f9b9384e801d","name":"Kristi","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/#\\/schema\\/person\\/image\\/","url":"https:\\/\\/secure.gravatar.com\\/avatar\\/a056597af5f6885fa21448efda40a062e149f03ef2bc619db73c4db500f2db0d?s=96&d=mm&r=g","contentUrl":"https:\\/\\/secure.gravatar.com\\/avatar\\/a056597af5f6885fa21448efda40a062e149f03ef2bc619db73c4db500f2db0d?s=96&d=mm&r=g","caption":"Kristi"},"sameAs":["https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/about-me\\/"]},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#faq-question-1691085282993","position":1,"url":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#faq-question-1691085282993","name":"Is parmesan cheese vegetarian?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Some parmesan has rennet and is therefore not vegetarian. Be sure to buy vegetarian parmesan if you want to keep the soup vegetarian.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#faq-question-1692026331353","position":2,"url":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#faq-question-1692026331353","name":"What are the benefits of lentils?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"White beans are high in fiber and vitamins such as magnesium and zinc. They are also a good plant based protein source.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#faq-question-1729621560710","position":3,"url":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#faq-question-1729621560710","name":"Can I make this soup vegan?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, use vegan parmesan or omit.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Recipe","name":"Tuscan Lentil Soup with Sundried Tomatoes","author":{"@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/#\\/schema\\/person\\/9672699ccfbdf3802f89f9b9384e801d"},"description":"This Tuscan Lentil Soup with Sundried Tomatoes is a delicious healthy soup recipe.","datePublished":"2024-12-11T20:05:59+00:00","image":["https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/12\\/IMG_2024-12-10-135820.jpeg","https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/12\\/IMG_2024-12-10-135820-500x500.jpeg","https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/12\\/IMG_2024-12-10-135820-500x375.jpeg","https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/12\\/IMG_2024-12-10-135820-480x270.jpeg"],"recipeYield":["3"],"prepTime":"PT5M","cookTime":"PT27M","recipeIngredient":["3 tablespoons olive oil","1 small onion - finely chopped","2 medium carrots - finely chopped","3 stalks celery - finely chopped","6 cloves garlic - minced","1 8 oz jar sundried tomatoes - drained","2 tablespoons tomato paste","1 teaspoon salt (adjust to your saltiness preference but I found 1 teaspoon to be best)","black pepper to taste (I used about 1\\/4 teaspoon)","1\\/2 teaspoon red pepper flakes (optional - omit if you don&#39;t like spice)","1 teaspoon paprika","1 teaspoon dried thyme","1 teaspoon dried oregano","5-6 cups vegetable or chicken broth* (use bone broth for extra protein )","1\\/2 cup finely chopped basil","1\\/3 cup fresh grated parmesan","3\\/4 cup dried brown or green lentils","2 cups finely chopped kale or green of choice"],"recipeInstructions":[{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add oil to a soup pot over medium heat. Add onion and cook for 5 minutes. Add sundried tomatoes, garlic, tomato pate, celery and carrots. Stir everything together and cook for another 5 minutes.","name":"Add oil to a soup pot over medium heat. Add onion and cook for 5 minutes. Add sundried tomatoes, garlic, tomato pate, celery and carrots. Stir everything together and cook for another 5 minutes.","url":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#wprm-recipe-12305-step-0-0"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add all remaining ingredients except for the kale to the pot. Stir to combine. Bring to a boil and then lower to a simmer. Cook for 25-30 minutes, until lentils have softened but still have texture. Turn off heat.","name":"Add all remaining ingredients except for the kale to the pot. Stir to combine. Bring to a boil and then lower to a simmer. Cook for 25-30 minutes, until lentils have softened but still have texture. Turn off heat.","url":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#wprm-recipe-12305-step-0-1"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Optional step: If you want your soup to be creamier add 2 cups to a blender and blend until smooth. Add the blender soup back to the pot. Alternatively you can partially blend the soup with an immersion blender.","name":"Optional step: If you want your soup to be creamier add 2 cups to a blender and blend until smooth. Add the blender soup back to the pot. Alternatively you can partially blend the soup with an immersion blender.","url":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#wprm-recipe-12305-step-0-2"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add kale to the pot and stir until wilted. Divide out and serve.","name":"Add kale to the pot and stir until wilted. Divide out and serve.","url":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#wprm-recipe-12305-step-0-3"}],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"5","ratingCount":"5","reviewCount":"5"},"review":[{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"reviewBody":"I reduced the fat, added more veggies and basil, some whole wheat angel hair, and used some cooked lentils I needed to use up. It was soooo good! Thank you! Adding this to the soup rotation :)","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Phoebe"},"datePublished":"2026-01-23"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"reviewBody":"Thank you Claudia! I can add that note to the recipe.","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Kristi"},"datePublished":"2025-12-11"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"reviewBody":"Really flavorful soup! I think the salt should be added at the very end, to taste, with all the punchy flavors (sun-dried tom and parm) in it. Other than that, superb!","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"claudia"},"datePublished":"2025-12-11"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"reviewBody":"Love this soup! Very customizable as well, we usually add some chicken in. Great tip about blending the soup, I usually fish out the tomatoes to blend them up and add it back in so there are no big chunks. Stays well in the fridge and is even more flavorful the next day!","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Alex"},"datePublished":"2025-04-27"},{"@type":"Review","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","ratingValue":"5"},"reviewBody":"Very good soup. The sun dried tomatoes give it a nice depth of flavor. I threw the parmesan rind in too, cos that\'s just what I do. Substituted spinach for kale cos hate kale. Will definitely make again:)","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Tee"},"datePublished":"2024-12-14"}],"recipeCategory":["dinner"],"recipeCuisine":["american italian fusion","vegetarian"],"keywords":"tuscan lentil soup with sundried tomatoes","nutrition":{"@type":"NutritionInformation","calories":"447 kcal","carbohydrateContent":"41 g","proteinContent":"33 g","fatContent":"18 g","saturatedFatContent":"4 g","cholesterolContent":"8 mg","sodiumContent":"1235 mg","fiberContent":"18 g","sugarContent":"6 g","unsaturatedFatContent":"13 g","servingSize":"1 serving"},"@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#recipe","isPartOf":{"@id":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/#article"},"mainEntityOfPage":"https:\\/\\/avocadoskillet.com\\/tuscan-lentil-soup-with-sundried-tomatoes\\/"}]}',
            'image' => 'https://avocadoskillet.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/IMG_2024-12-10-135841.jpeg',
        'ingredients' => '["3 tablespoons olive oil","1 small onion - finely chopped","2 medium carrots - finely chopped","3 stalks celery - finely chopped","6 cloves garlic - minced","1 8 oz jar sundried tomatoes - drained","2 tablespoons tomato paste","1 teaspoon salt (adjust to your saltiness preference but I found 1 teaspoon to be best)","black pepper to taste (I used about 1\\/4 teaspoon)","1\\/2 teaspoon red pepper flakes (optional - omit if you don&#39;t like spice)","1 teaspoon paprika","1 teaspoon dried thyme","1 teaspoon dried oregano","5-6 cups vegetable or chicken broth* (use bone broth for extra protein )","1\\/2 cup finely chopped basil","1\\/3 cup fresh grated parmesan","3\\/4 cup dried brown or green lentils","2 cups finely chopped kale or green of choice"]',
            'directions' => '["Add oil to a soup pot over medium heat. Add onion and cook for 5 minutes. Add sundried tomatoes, garlic, tomato pate, celery and carrots. Stir everything together and cook for another 5 minutes.","Add all remaining ingredients except for the kale to the pot. Stir to combine. Bring to a boil and then lower to a simmer. Cook for 25-30 minutes, until lentils have softened but still have texture. Turn off heat.","Optional step: If you want your soup to be creamier add 2 cups to a blender and blend until smooth. Add the blender soup back to the pot. Alternatively you can partially blend the soup with an immersion blender.","Add kale to the pot and stir until wilted. Divide out and serve."]',
            'nutrition' => '[{"@type":"NutritionInformation","calories":"447 kcal","carbohydrateContent":"41 g","proteinContent":"33 g","fatContent":"18 g","saturatedFatContent":"4 g","cholesterolContent":"8 mg","sodiumContent":"1235 mg","fiberContent":"18 g","sugarContent":"6 g","unsaturatedFatContent":"13 g","servingSize":"1 serving"}]',
