mekitchenadventures.com\\/#website","url":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/","name":"Monkey and Me Kitchen Adventures","description":"Healthy Oil Free Whole Food Plant Based Recipes","publisher":{"@id":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/#organization"},"potentialAction":[{"@type":"SearchAction","target":{"@type":"EntryPoint","urlTemplate":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/?s={search_term_string}"},"query-input":{"@type":"PropertyValueSpecification","valueRequired":true,"valueName":"search_term_string"}}],"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Organization","@id":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/#organization","name":"Monkey and Me Kitchen Adventures","url":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/#\\/schema\\/logo\\/image\\/","url":"","contentUrl":"","caption":"Monkey and Me Kitchen Adventures"},"image":{"@id":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/#\\/schema\\/logo\\/image\\/"},"sameAs":["https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures","https:\\/\\/x.com\\/kitchnadventure","https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures\\/","https:\\/\\/www.pinterest.com\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures\\/","https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/channel\\/UCNwVMuueT_BUyl7-AOwpjYQ?view_as=subscriber"]},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/#\\/schema\\/person\\/00bad697c0d574b3e3164dbd231d87d5","name":"Ameera and Robin","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","inLanguage":"en-US","@id":"https:\\/\\/secure.gravatar.com\\/avatar\\/b1802613c7cecba57141906c11fa9a6324659679ac1adf2c2283f0b6e6b7093b?s=96&d=mm&r=g","url":"https:\\/\\/secure.gravatar.com\\/avatar\\/b1802613c7cecba57141906c11fa9a6324659679ac1adf2c2283f0b6e6b7093b?s=96&d=mm&r=g","contentUrl":"https:\\/\\/secure.gravatar.com\\/avatar\\/b1802613c7cecba57141906c11fa9a6324659679ac1adf2c2283f0b6e6b7093b?s=96&d=mm&r=g","caption":"Ameera and Robin"},"sameAs":["https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com"],"url":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/author\\/ameera-and-robin\\/"},{"@context":"https:\\/\\/schema.org\\/","@type":"Recipe","name":"Italian Broccolini Millet Bowl","description":"Bursting with spring, sunshiney flavors and feels, this easy and nutrient-packed Italian Broccolini Millet Bowl with Lemony Parsley Sauce is full of beautiful flavor, satisfying goodness, and superfood nourishment. \\u00a0Perfectly seasoned broccolini, peas, and cannelloni beans with chewy, nutty millet; drizzled with a Lemony Parsley Sauce (aka dream sauce); and sprinkled with vegan parm and lemon zest takes this bountiful bowl to the next level of fresh, wholesome goodness \\u2013 total veggie paradise!\\r\\n\\r\\nWhole Food Plant Based, vegan, plant based, oil free, refined sugar free, no highly processed ingredients, and gluten free.","author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Monkey and Me Kitchen Adventures"},"image":["https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/Italian-Broccolini-Millet-Bowl-with-Lemony-Parsley-Sauce_04-225x225.jpg","https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/Italian-Broccolini-Millet-Bowl-with-Lemony-Parsley-Sauce_04-260x195.jpg","https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/Italian-Broccolini-Millet-Bowl-with-Lemony-Parsley-Sauce_04-320x180.jpg","https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/Italian-Broccolini-Millet-Bowl-with-Lemony-Parsley-Sauce_04.jpg"],"url":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/italian-broccolini-millet-bowl-with-lemony-parsley-sauce\\/","recipeIngredient":["2\\/3 cup\\u00a0red onion, fine dice","2\\/3 cup red bell pepper, fine dice","1 Tablespoon minced\\u00a0garlic","8 to 10 oz. broccolini\\u00a0(or tiny broccoli florets)","3 Tablespoons lemon juice","1\\/3 to \\u00bd cup water","1 teaspoon miso","1 \\u2013 15 oz. can\\u00a0cannelloni beans, drained and rinsed","1 cup frozen peas","1 \\u00bd cups cooked millet\\u00a0(or barley, couscous, quinoa etc.)","\\u00bd teaspoon onion powder","\\u00bd teaspoon garlic powder","\\u00bd teaspoon\\u00a0dried thyme leaves *","2 teaspoons\\u00a0Italian Seasoning","Pinch\\u00a0coriander","\\u00bd teaspoon sea salt\\u00a0(+\\/- to taste) *","\\u00bc teaspoon black pepper","Italian Lemony Parsley Sauce (See recipe below)","Vegan Parmesan Cheese (optional)","\\u00bd teaspoon of fresh lemon zest\\u00a0(optional)"],"recipeInstructions":[{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Cook the millet (or barley, quinoa, etc.) per package directions.\\u00a0 Set aside.","url":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/italian-broccolini-millet-bowl-with-lemony-parsley-sauce\\/#instruction-step-1"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Make the Lemony Parsley Sauce\\u00a0(see recipe below in blog post).","url":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/italian-broccolini-millet-bowl-with-lemony-parsley-sauce\\/#instruction-step-2"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"In a large ceramic\\/enamel-lined Dutch oven, skillet or similar stock pot, add the red onion and red bell peppers, saut\\u00e9 over medium-high heat for several minutes. Then add the minced garlic, saut\\u00e9 for 30 seconds, then add the lemon juice, water, miso, and all the Spice\\/Herb ingredients, stir to combine.","url":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/italian-broccolini-millet-bowl-with-lemony-parsley-sauce\\/#instruction-step-3"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"Add the frozen peas, cannelloni beans, then lay the broccolini (cut off and discard the touch ends) on top, increase the heat until boiling, then immediately lower to a simmer, cover with a lid, and cook until the broccolini reaches the desired tenderness. Add additional water by the Tablespoon as the water evaporates.","url":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/italian-broccolini-millet-bowl-with-lemony-parsley-sauce\\/#instruction-step-4"},{"@type":"HowToStep","text":"To assemble, place some cooked millet (or cooked quinoa, barley, etc.) in a bowl, add the seasoned beans\\/pea mixture, then lay the broccolini on top. Drizzle with the Lemony Parsley Sauce, sprinkle some Vegan Parmesan Cheese, and a tiny sprinkle of lemon zest.","url":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/italian-broccolini-millet-bowl-with-lemony-parsley-sauce\\/#instruction-step-5"}],"prepTime":"PT10M","cookTime":"PT15M","totalTime":"PT-495529H5M35S","recipeYield":["4","4 Servings"],"recipeCategory":"Dinner","cookingMethod":"Stovetop","recipeCuisine":"Italian","nutrition":{"servingSize":"A bowl","calories":"442 calories","sugarContent":"6.4 g","sodiumContent":"73.1 mg","fatContent":"4.3 g","saturatedFatContent":"0.6 g","transFatContent":"0 g","carbohydrateContent":"83 g","fiberContent":"16.4 g","proteinContent":"18.1 g","cholesterolContent":"0 mg","@type":"nutritionInformation"},"datePublished":"2019-03-18","@id":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/italian-broccolini-millet-bowl-with-lemony-parsley-sauce\\/#recipe","isPartOf":{"@id":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/italian-broccolini-millet-bowl-with-lemony-parsley-sauce\\/#article"},"mainEntityOfPage":"https:\\/\\/monkeyandmekitchenadventures.com\\/italian-broccolini-millet-bowl-with-lemony-parsley-sauce\\/"}]}',
